relation: The offer many different extracurricular activities such as sports, drama, art, speech, school politics, etc. There is something for everyone who wants to get involved.
The school has an excellent cafeteria food that is prepared by culinary art students at the school.
There are no dorms, it is a day school.
As long as you study hard and do your best, then you'll do great at this school.

A friendly and inviting campus that offers a comfortable transition from high school to college. Overall, the teachers are willing to assist the students and provide help when needed. It is a great place to complete prerequisite classes before transferring to a 4 year University.
